(<em>Photo credit: George OURFALIAN/AFP</em>).</p>
<p>A Syrian soldier poses for a photo in front of a large poster of Syrian President Bashar al-Assad outside the Aleppo Citadel on January 22, 2017. <br />
<em>(Photo credit: LOUAI BESHARA/AFP/Getty Images).</em></p>
<p>Forces loyal to the Syrian regime celebrate with national flags after Syria's army and allied forces took full control from rebel groups of the strategic town of Salma. <br />
<em>(Photo credit: STRINGER/AFP/Getty Images).</em></p>
<p>A Syrian soldier walks towards a fluttering Syrian flag on a roof at a government forces' position in the village of Hawshariya. <br />
<em>(Photo credit: GEORGE OURFALIAN/AFP/Getty Images).</em></p>
